               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa tägänǝyo “Book of thanksgiving” (fols. 2ra-16va)(cp. EMML nos.
                     1835, 1841, 4268)&#xD; I-1) Introduction (fols. 2ra-3ra)&#xD; I-2) Homily by an
                     anonymous author on Archangel Michael (fols. 3rb-16va)&#xD; I-3) Taʾammǝra
                     Mikāʾel “Miracles of Michael”: 17 miracles (fols. 16va-38vb), incomplete&#xD;
                     &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
